name: 2023 6th International Conference on Software and Services Engineering
content: Publication: As ICSSE 2023 is the workshop of ICGDA 2023, all registered papers will be published in the International Conference Proceedings Series titled ICGDA 2023 . All papers will be archived in the Online Digital Library, and submitted to Ei Compendex and Scopus for index and submitted to be reviewed by Thomson Reuters Conference Proceedings Citation Index (ISI Web of Science).
